name: Royal Jelly: The Tale of the Time Traveling Lesbeean, the Adventures She Undertook, and What Happened To Her Hence
name_original: Royal Jelly: The Tale of the Time Traveling Lesbeean, the Adventures She Undertook, and What Happened To Her Hence
description:
A chill game by some cool people for a rad game jam. Said cool people are:

Ashley Fisher: Programming
Bobby Lang: Game design, lead writing, the karaoke song
Jeff Brice: Music, puns
MacKenzie Rawcliffe: Visual design, writing, CSS
Madeleine Appelmans: Art, map design

SEO: BEES, HONEY, ROYAL JELLY, TIME TRAVEL, LOVE, TAXIDERMY
